[p 
	"[
	[a id=1 
	]a
	[a href=#r1 
		"1
	]a
	"]
	": I cross the goal of Neo Green Hill 1 in 9.57 seconds, but get
	$LF
	"a level time of 0:12:85 because I have to wait for the camera to
	$LF
	"catch up for the goal sprite to load. Since I outran the camera at
	$LF
	"the earliest possible moment, and stayed offscreen until the level 
	$LF
	"ended, I believe 0:12:85 is the fastest time possible on that level. 
	$LF
	"Note that time bonus on this and several other levels actually takes 
	$LF
	"longer to count down than the entire level took to complete (too bad 
	$LF
	"the countdown is unskippable).
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"[
	[a id=2 
	]a
	[a href=#r2 
		"2
	]a
	"]
	": The game doesn't display this time because it replaces the timer 
	$LF
	"with a 5-minute countdown at the first rocket transition. To see that
	$LF
	"the time was 0:53:25, I hex-edited the completed level into the
	$LF
	""time attack" mode of the game on that level. I did find a way to 
	$LF
	"skip the first transition and beat the level before the rocket even 
	$LF
	"takes off, but it was slower overall.
	$LF
]p
